divs: Sighting Details I saw some cool looking clouds from a storm front, so I got out my Olympus camera and took some pictures and video. When I looked at them on the computer, I saw what looks like a flying saucer in one of the pictures and a fast moving object in the video. I slowed the video down to 1 tenth speed to try and determine if it was a bird. There appears to be several white spots under the photo with maybe a funnel like affect. The video could be a bird, but it would have to be dive bombing really fast down from the clouds.
